{
  "stem": "19921.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was strictly extermination, one of the first one, which, as far as I remember, was initiated in December of 1941-- very, very primitive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started with this thing here until they develop those big camps like Auschwitz and the other ones.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the way we, we were told is that there were-- people were brought there by buses, and that they were parked overnight in a church and stripped of their clothing and loaded into a special bus, which 50 or 75 people were able to get in there, and the gas was released in a short time, which took about 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was something like 15 kilometers, something like that, to that forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the time that bus reached the station there, the people were dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The church absolutely was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The church was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later, of course, I saw that the-- on pictures, on the video pictures here, that the church is still standing and they're still praying in that church.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That church is still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what did I saw?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of bones-- a lot of bones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of bones were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, again, graves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a lot of big graves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mass graves they had there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were, again, a lot of ashes, a lot of ash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And again, we were told that people were buried in that thing here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were no-- now, this camp was operating actually to the last-- to the last time for the occupation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, we, we entered-- as far as I know, we entered on the 25th or the 26th or something like in the 20s of January, that camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that camp was still in production.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That camp was still in production.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Germans were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Germans were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
